{
  "stem": "21437.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he just said-- he examined me, and he said, I am not buying this, that you won't have a child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not buying this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Something is there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If it is physical-- whatever it is, you have to do certain things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm going to tell you what you do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he told me about conception.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He explained to me certain things-- very simple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Very-- he said what people-- anyhow, whatever it is, he explained to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And things, which in the Jewish religion, when there is a certain time of the month, you-- you-- you know, if you try to conceive, it is really something, which is really a long story.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I won't-- OK, I want to make it short.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So what happened, that I listened to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you know-- and he was so good to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, he was just watching over me, like a-- and somehow, I got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But then I got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, you see, I told you so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But now it was-- this what I was told, that I would-- so I was-- this, I couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because I was told by so many specialists, in Israel and here, that I won't be able to have a child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So even, no matter what, so it was a most-- it was just as terrible a time during the pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because the fear-- I was in-- I was fearful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Even when I was asleep, I could reach out and touch that fear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was sort of trying to-- you know, sort of-- I was trying to-- to envelop this embryo, when it was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I went through that third-- and the doctor, Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Meyer, said to me, so I had to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
